nodes.text: Irresistible: The Voices of Star Wars Resistance

Irresistible: The Voices of Star Wars Resistance is an interview of Christopher Sean and Suzie McGrath, published in Star Wars Insider 186 on December 18, 2018. The article discusses the creation, character traits, and connections to the actors that characters Kazuda Xiono and Tamara Ryvora had, as well as promote the upcoming Disney Channel television show, Star Wars Resistance. Sean and McGrath's backgrounds in acting and voice acting, as well as their background with Star Wars, is discussed as well.
